  "body": "<figure>\n\n\n<img src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1598684832811-SZW5G6F5GZEIG2LUT3MD/16a-jacksplayroom.jpg\"/>\n\n\n</figure>\n\n\n<p>While creating <a href=\"http://wp.me/p4uKLp-6tF\">this world map wall decal</a> as well as <a href=\"http://wp.me/p4uKLp-6to\">this door sign</a>, I thought I may as well make a little sign for Jack's playroom. I used <a href=\"http://www.silhouetteamerica.com/shop/&amp;aff_id=Mk4NE4JGfCx5y:TOY6$O:A&amp;ad_id=15\">my Silhouette</a> and the <a href=\"http://www.silhouetteamerica.com/june/&amp;aff_id=Mk4NE4JGfCx5y:TOY6$O:A&amp;ad_id=1\">Silhouette Studio</a> software to create a wall decal with white vinyl.</p>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n<img alt=\"16b-IMG_3350.jpg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1598684879902-AN04AN0JS0S9DMX1OIXU/16b-IMG_3350.jpg\">\n</img>\n\n<img alt=\"16c-.jpg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1598684879954-VFYX9XL84NSHBJDN6488/16c-.jpg\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"16d-IMG_3361.jpg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1598684880840-A8YDZ4UISGZHB3KZI2L8/16d-IMG_3361.jpg\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"16e-IMG_3357.jpg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1598684881004-RHE7V1RUR3ZG5F9D1QIY/16e-IMG_3357.jpg\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"16f-IMG_3354.jpg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1598684881351-4ODVEAP23Y3V80NOUA97/16f-IMG_3354.jpg\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"16g-IMG_3364.jpg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1598684881582-XXE2H6HUAM0E2UFS1S1E/16g-IMG_3364.jpg\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"16h-IMG_3367.jpg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1598684881987-IHAW4W2IELYDAK4TH2BO/16h-IMG_3367.jpg\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"16i-jack_playroom.jpg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1598684882108-0BNQXDZ7TGMUOJD3YN7X/16i-jack_playroom.jpg\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"16j-IMG_3379.jpg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1598684882739-M0GY5UD4TMR9289BYF9E/16j-IMG_3379.jpg\"/>\n\n\n\n\n<p>Now that I am clearly hooked on creating wall decals, any suggestions on what I should make next?</p>"
